OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778371373
OL,3,CHungary's Peter Magyar sworn in as PM,
OL,4,Cending Viktor Orban's 16-year rule
OL,6,FHungary's Peter Magyar took his oath
OL,7,Fof office on Saturday to become the
OL,8,Fcountry's new prime minister, ending
OL,9,FViktor Orban's 16 years of
OL,10,Fauthoritarian rule.
OL,12,FMagyar's centre-right Tisza party
OL,13,Fdefeated Orban's nationalist-populist
OL,14,FFidesz in a stunning blow last month,
OL,15,Fgaining more votes and seats in
OL,16,Fparliament than any other party in
OL,17,FHungary's post-Communist history.
OL,26,@kD@LrrlD@RrpnD@LrrqD@KrpuD@Mrp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
