OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778371373
OL,3,CHungary's Peter Magyar sworn in as PM,
OL,4,Cending Viktor Orban's 16-year rule
OL,6,FThe win, which gave Tisza a two-thirds
OL,7,Fparliamentary majority, will allow it
OL,8,Fto roll back many of the policies that
OL,9,Fgave Orban a reputation among his
OL,10,Fcritics as a far-right authoritarian.
OL,12,FIn a speech to lawmakers in Hungary's
OL,13,Fparliament after being sworn in,
OL,14,FMagyar said he would not use his
OL,15,Foffice to "rule" Hungary, "but to
OL,16,Fserve my homeland".
OL,26,@kD@LrrlD@RrpqD@IrpwD@KOUwD@PO]wD@[OUxD@
OL,26,ARO]
