OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778371373
OL,3,CHungary's Peter Magyar sworn in as PM,
OL,4,Cending Viktor Orban's 16-year rule
OL,6,F"I'm not standing here because I'm
OL,7,Fdifferent from anyone else in the
OL,8,Fcountry," Magyar said. "I stand here
OL,9,Fbecause millions of Hungarians decided
OL,10,Fthat they want change.
OL,12,F"And this trust that we have received
OL,13,Fis both a weight of honour and a moral
OL,14,Fobligation, but also a wonderful
OL,15,Ffeeling."
OL,17,FMagyar has vowed to restore democratic
OL,18,Finstitutions and governmental checks
OL,19,Fand balances that were heavily eroded
OL,20,Fduring Orban's rule, and to clamp down
OL,21,Fon alleged corruption.
OL,26,@kD@LrrlD@RrpnD@AOUpD@IO]pD@XOUtD@AOUwD@
OL,26,AIO]|D@Krp
