CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778371373
OL,3,CHungary's Peter Magyar sworn in as PM,
OL,4,Cending Viktor Orban's 16-year rule
OL,6,FMagyar earlier called on Hungarians to
OL,7,Fattend an all-day "regime-change"
OL,8,Fcelebration on Kossuth Square outside
OL,9,Fparliament to mark his inauguration
OL,10,Fand the end of the Orban era.
OL,12,FThousands had already gathered in the
OL,13,Fsquare as the new representatives were
OL,14,Fsworn in, many waving Hungarian and EU
OL,15,Fflags and wearing Tisza T-shirts.
OL,17,FThe new prime minister was set to
OL,18,Faddress the crowd outside after the
OL,19,Fcompletion of parliament's inaugural
OL,20,Fsession.
OL,26,@kD@LrrlD@RrpoD@SOUoD@aO]rD@Wrp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
