OL,3,CHungary's Peter Magyar sworn in as PM,
OL,4,Cending Viktor Orban's 16-year rule
OL,6,FHungary's new national assembly has 54
OL,7,Fwomen lawmakers, most from the Tisza
OL,8,Fparty ` more than a quarter of the
OL,9,Ftotal and the most in Hungary's
OL,10,Fhistory.
OL,12,FOne attendee, Andrea Szepesi, an
OL,13,Feconomist from Budapest, said it was
OL,14,F"about time" that more female
OL,15,Flawmakers held seats in parliament.
OL,17,FUnder Orban's rule, there were fewer
OL,18,Fwomen in government than in nearly all
OL,19,Fof the EU's other 26 nations.
OL,26,@kD@LrrlD@RrpvD@AOUvD@LO]yD@Jrp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
