PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778371373
OL,3,CHungary's Peter Magyar sworn in as PM,
OL,4,Cending Viktor Orban's 16-year rule
OL,6,F"Finally, women are able to
OL,7,Fparticipate in this new, beautiful
OL,8,Fdemocratic system and the flourishing
OL,9,Fof the country," she said.
OL,11,FMagyar has promised to repair his
OL,12,Fcountry's ties with the EU, which
OL,13,FOrban had pushed to a breaking point,
OL,14,Fand to restore Hungary's place among
OL,15,FWestern democracies, whose standing
OL,16,Fhad been called into question as Orban
OL,17,Fdrifted ever closer to Russia.
OL,26,@kD@LrrlD@RrpnD@AOUqD@PO]uD@DrpxD@erp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
