OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778371373
OL,3,CHungary's Peter Magyar sworn in as PM,
OL,4,Cending Viktor Orban's 16-year rule
OL,6,FThe EU flag was raised on the
OL,7,Fparliament building's facade Saturday
OL,8,Fafternoon for the first time since
OL,9,FOrban's government removed it in 2014.
OL,11,FUnlocking about 17 billion euros
OL,12,F(around #14.7 billion) of EU funds for
OL,13,FHungary frozen during Orban's time in
OL,14,Foffice over rule-of-law and corruption
OL,15,Fconcerns is among the incoming prime
OL,16,Fminister's top priorities.
