OL,3,CHungary's Peter Magyar sworn in as PM,
OL,4,Cending Viktor Orban's 16-year rule
OL,6,FThe money is sorely needed to help
OL,7,Fjump-start Hungary's struggling
OL,8,Feconomy, which has stagnated for the
OL,9,Fpast four years.
OL,11,FMany of the nearly 3.4 million
OL,12,FHungarians that voted for Tisza expect
OL,13,FMagyar to hold Fidesz officials and
OL,14,Ftheir business allies accountable for
OL,15,Fthe perceived misconduct of the
OL,16,Foutgoing administration.
OL,26,@kD@LrrlD@Rrp
