OL,3,CHungary's Peter Magyar sworn in as PM,
OL,4,Cending Viktor Orban's 16-year rule
OL,6,FMagyar plans to form a National Asset
OL,7,FRecovery and Protection Office, an
OL,8,Fauthority tasked with investigating
OL,9,Fand seeking to recover public funds
OL,10,Fmisused during Orban's tenure.
OL,12,FHe's also vowed to suspend the news
OL,13,Fservices of Hungary's public
OL,14,Fbroadcaster ` widely seen as a
OL,15,Fmouthpiece of Orban's party ` until
OL,16,Fobjectivity can be restored.
OL,26,@kD@LrrlD@RrprD@SrpwD@Rrp
