OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778371373
OL,3,CHungary's Peter Magyar sworn in as PM,
OL,4,Cending Viktor Orban's 16-year rule
OL,6,FIn his speech to lawmakers Saturday,
OL,7,FMagyar referenced his intentions to
OL,8,Fhold former officials accountable for
OL,9,Fpast abuses, saying voters had "given
OL,10,Fus a mandate to open a new chapter in
OL,11,FHungary's history.
OL,13,F"We must understand, however, that
OL,14,Fthere can be no new beginning without
OL,15,Freconciliation," he said. "There can
OL,16,Fbe no reconciliation without justice.
OL,17,FAnd there can be no justice without
OL,18,Fconfronting the past."
OL,26,@kD@LrrlD@RrpqD@`OUuD@AOUwD@PO]wD@[OUzD@
